      },
      "rationale": "All 11 simulation runs converged within 50 Newton-Raphson iterations per load step. Residual norms fell below 1e-6 for all cases. No solver warnings or ill-conditioning flags were observed. Energy balance checked post-solution. Gradation 2 achieved: convergence criteria documented and verified for all runs."
