        "description": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric (ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3) with acceptance threshold E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% for all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm)."
      },
      "rationale": "All three QoIs pass both acceptance criteria: stiffness (E/uval = 1.21, diff = 4.8%), yield force (E/uval = 0.87, diff = 3.1%), force at 40 mm (E/uval = 1.54, diff = 6.2%). Comparison methodology follows ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3 with combined experimental and simulation uncertainty in the denominator. Gradation 3 achieved: quantitative metric-based comparison with pre-defined acceptance thresholds."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
